snippet.title: I Stand By Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
There is a mountain of evidence that Amber Heard physically abused Johnny Depp but has accused Depp of abusing her. Even though there isn't any evidence of Johnny abusing Heard, or anyone else, a judge in a London case ruled against Depp. This page is dedicated to providing evidence of Depp's innocence and providing proof of Heard's lies.

It is very important for the facts of this case to be revealed because with the mountain of evidence proving Depp's innocence and with all his high powered lawyers and plenty of money to pay for them and court, if he is found guilty in a Virginia court case in 2021, then how are the rest of us whom have been victims of abuse can ever have hope that justice will be served.  

Please join me on providing and proving that Johnny Depp is innocent along with anything else that pertains to Depp.

I stand by Johnny

#JusticeForJohnnyDepp
